Demo Challenge Ideas
====================

Points of Discussion
-------------------
The main thing a robot contribues with in a smart home is manipulation.

The main thing that got points in the robocup scenario was sensors

Ideas
=====
 - same as the previous demo but then improved
 - open a fridge, check fridge with live webcam
 - ClickOn system to trigger electronic stuff
    - set coffee, pick up the cup and deliver
    - set tea, pour and deliver
 - Philips Hue
     - trigger based on position in room
     - trigger
 - more emphasis on the App
     - queue skill server commands
